nda, Hakim Ziyech, Khalid  Boutaib.<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"398","checkdouble":"189115"},{"date":"04:44 21/06","title":"Th\u1eafng ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran, HLV TBN c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/thang-chat-vat-truoc-iran-hlv-tbn-canh-bao-cac-hoc-tro.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Fernando Hierro ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Iran vs TBN, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 50 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf B\u00f2 t\u00f3t c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n \u0111i s\u00e2u \u1edf World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">TBN ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n Iran r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ec1u tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eadm. Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fernando Hierro ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Iran vs TBN h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Fernando Hierro ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Iran vs TBN h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/Fernando-Hierro-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Iran-vs-TBN-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Diego Costa gi\u00fap TBN gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1edd b\u00e0n th\u1eafng may m\u1eafn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Iran khi\u1ebfn TBN g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, La Roja ch\u1ec9 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch c\u00f3 1 l\u1ea7n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ea7y may m\u1eafn.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00fat 54, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 b\u00ean ph\u00eda Iran trong n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1eadp v\u00e0o ch\u00e2n Diego Costa bay th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap TBN ch\u01a1i kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc, kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady h\u1ecd c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ec3 Iran d\u1ed3n \u00e9p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng treo b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Iran t\u1eeb hai bi\u00ean khi\u1ebfn TBN g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, song r\u1ea5t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecd v\u1eabn b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-iran-vs-tay-ban-nha-421-189095.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Iran vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha </span>gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u c\u00f3 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 tr\u1eadn, \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p Ma R\u1ed1c, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Sergio Ramos v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV TBN c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Fernando Hierro ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Iran vs TBN, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 50 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf B\u00f2 t\u00f3t c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n \u0111i s\u00e2u \u1edf World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fernando Hierro phat bieu ve tran Iran vs TBN\" title=\"Fernando Hierro ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Iran vs TBN\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/thang-chat-vat-truoc-iran-hlv-tbn-canh-bao-cac-hoc-tro.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Fernando Hierro ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Iran vs TBN</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, Iran \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd, l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd khi\u1ebfn TBN kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 b\u1edfi TBN \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, c\u00f2n v\u1ec1 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00e2y Ban Nha mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay, mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t d\u1ea7n l\u00ean trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"397","checkdouble":"189117"},{"date":"05:00 21/06","title":"HLV Iran cay c\u00fa sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea7y cay \u0111\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc TBN","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/hlv-iran-cay-cu-sau-that-bai-day-cay-dang-truoc-tbn.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Carlos Queiroz ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Iran vs TBN, HLV c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1 t\u1ecf ra ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i sau khi Iran kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc La Roja.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Iran ch\u01a1i ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u01b0\u1edbc TBN</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ma R\u1ed1c, Iran h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi TBN v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i t\u1eed th\u1ee7, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n La Roja sau 45 ph\u00fat b\u00f3ng l\u0103n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Carlos Queiroz ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Iran vs TBN h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Carlos Queiroz ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Iran vs TBN h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/HLV-Carlos-Queiroz-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Iran-vs-TBN-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Iran thua TBN 0-1 b\u1edfi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng may m\u1eafn c\u1ee7a Costa</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, ngay \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2, Iran \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua b\u1edfi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng thi\u1ebfu may m\u1eafn. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Iran ph\u00e1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1eadp ch\u00e2n Diego Costa bay th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Beiranvand.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn Iran \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ed3n l\u00ean t\u00ecm b\u00e0n g\u1ee1, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n David de Gea, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng treo b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb bi\u00ean v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Iran kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Thua 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc TBN, c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u1eabn c\u00f2n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi B\u0110N \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i cho m\u1ed9t t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Carlos Queiroz ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi Iran thua tr\u1eadn</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Carlos Queiroz ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Iran vs TBN, HLV c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1 t\u1ecf ra ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i sau khi Iran kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc La Roja.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Iran\" title=\"HLV Iran\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/hlv-iran-cay-cu-sau-that-bai-day-cay-dang-truoc-tbn.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Carlos Queiroz cho r\u1eb1ng Iran x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc TBN</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u00f4m nay ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t. Iran \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y run s\u1ee3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-iran-01-tay-ban-nha-bo-tot-run-ray-gianh-3-diem-421-189120.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/du-am-iran-01-tay-ban-nha-bo-tot-run-ray-gianh-3-diem.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-iran-01-tay-ban-nha-bo-tot-run-ray-gianh-3-diem-421-189120.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Iran 0-1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha: \u201cB\u00f2 t\u00f3t\u201d run r\u1ea9y gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m</span><br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Iran song T\u00e2y Ban Nha ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u. Tr\u1eadn Iran vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ea3ng B World Cup...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\u201cV\u1edbi th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd ra ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m, Iran x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong tr \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi B\u0110N. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi B\u0110N \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"396","checkdouble":"189118"},{"date":"04:13 21/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Iran 0-1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/TBN-an-mung-tran-thang-Iran-1-0.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Iran 0-1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 b\u1ea3ng B VCK World Cup 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n- Iran v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- D\u00f9 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi 81.6% trong hi\u1ec7p 1, T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ec9 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch \u0111\u00fang 1 l\u1ea7n (v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- C\u1ea3 Isco (55) v\u00e0 Sergio Ramos (53) \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i Iran (49) trong hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Iran 0-1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Iran 0-1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/TBN-vs-Iran-Costa-an-mung.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Costa l\u00e0 t\u00e1c gi\u1ea3 b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Iran 0-1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n- Diego Costa \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf c\u1ea3 3 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 Iran 0-1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Costa ghi 9 b\u00e0n sau 9 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t cho T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Iran ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 6 trong 7 l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u t\u1ea1i World Cup, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1eabn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 t\u1ea1i World Cup (th\u1eafng 3, h\u00f2a 2).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"TBN an mung tran thang Iran 1-0\" title=\"TBN an mung tran thang Iran 1-0\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/TBN-an-mung-tran-thang-Iran-1-0.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">TBN v\u1eabn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n- Isco c\u00f3 138 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng \u1edf tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran, nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t trong c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 TBN t\u1ea1i 1 tr\u1eadn World Cup t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1966 t\u1edbi nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- C\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a World Cup ng\u00e0y 20/6 (theo gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng) \u0111\u1ec1u k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 3 World Cup xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n 3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u00f9ng 1-0 trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y, sau 25/6/1982 v\u00e0 23/6/2010.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- 20 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 qua c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-0, l\u1ea7n duy nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1954 (26 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Iran 0-1 Tay Ban Nha\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Iran 0-1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/Thong-so-Iran.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Iran 0-1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Iran 0-1 TBN:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-iran-01-tay-ban-nha-bang-b-world-cup-2018-461-189115.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Iran 0-1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha (B\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-iran-vs-tay-ban-nha-421-189095.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Iran vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-iran-vs-tay-ban-nha-463-189091.html\">Iran 0-1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha (KT): Th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n v\u00e0 may m\u1eafn c\u1ee7a La Roja</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"395","checkdouble":"189119"},{"date":"04:22 21/06","title":"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Iran 0-1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha: \u201cB\u00f2 t\u00f3t\u201d run r\u1ea9y gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/du-am-iran-01-tay-ban-nha-bo-tot-run-ray-gianh-3-diem.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Iran song T\u00e2y Ban Nha ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u. Tr\u1eadn Iran vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh La Roja t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u1ebf t\u1eafc</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. La Roja l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn 67% v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Iran vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Iran vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/Du-am-Iran-vs-Tay-Ban-Nha-bang-B-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>TBN \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Iran r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 c\u00fa s\u00fat tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch th\u00ec T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 6 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng tr\u00fang khung th\u00e0nh. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a Ronaldo v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa hat-trick m\u1edbi gi\u00fap Seleccao c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n La Roja v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a 3-3.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 b\u1ea3ng B, T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p Iran. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1 ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ma R\u1ed1c khi ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 32%. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed trong hi\u1ec7p 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t \u1edf ph\u00fat 90+5 l\u1ea1i thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Iran. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Aziz Bouhaddouz trong m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng l\u00f9i v\u1ec1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u1ec1 l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0. Iran ch\u01a1i t\u1eed th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ma R\u1ed1c v\u1edbi hy v\u1ecdng gi\u00e0nh 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m song may m\u1eafn \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nIran b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi TBN v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng B sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, song r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u1ecd v\u1eabn \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi La Roja.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u00f3ng ch\u01b0a l\u0103n nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng ra vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf B\u00f2 t\u00f3t s\u1ebd d\u1ed3n \u00e9p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Iran c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tho\u00e1t thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat t\u1ea7m trung c\u1ee7a Ma R\u1ed1c, song kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ee1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc d\u00e0n sao si\u00eau h\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t ng\u1eabu h\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a TBN.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00fang nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, tr\u1eadn Iran vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh g\u1ed3m r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, TBN nhanh ch\u00f3ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLa Roja lu\u00f4n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng \u1edf m\u1ee9c 80%. Vi\u1ec7c Iran ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh La Roja d\u00e2ng l\u00ean r\u1ea5t cao.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"TBN choi tan cong be tac truoc Iran\" title=\"TBN ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u1ebf t\u1eafc tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/be-tac-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>TBN ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u1ebf t\u1eafc tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, b\u00f3ng ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn ch\u1ec9 l\u0103n b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Iran. Tuy nhi\u00ean, TBN d\u00f9 c\u1ea7m r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng. H\u1ecd tung ra 8 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m song ch\u1ec9 duy nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00e0n sao \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb x\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f2 kh\u00f4ng sao xuy\u00ean th\u1ee7ng n\u1ed5i h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee9ng nh\u01b0 b\u00ea t\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1. Diego Costa b\u1ecb phong t\u1ecfa&nbsp;ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng treo b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb bi\u00ean c\u1ee7a TBN c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111em l\u1ea1i k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1edfi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Iran c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nIsco v\u00e0 David Silva th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng sao ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1. Ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta l\u1ea1i ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn d\u00e0n sao c\u1ee7a B\u00f2 t\u00f3t b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1edd may m\u1eafn</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00ecm \u0111\u1ee7 m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u00ec b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng theo c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng ra.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Diego Costa giup TBN vuot len nho ban thang may man\" title=\"Diego Costa gi\u00fap TBN v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean nh\u1edd b\u00e0n th\u1eafng may m\u1eafn\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/costa.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Diego Costa gi\u00fap TBN v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean nh\u1edd b\u00e0n th\u1eafng may m\u1eafn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00fat 54, trong m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng l\u1ed9n x\u1ed9n trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m Iran, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1eadp ch\u00e2n Costa bay th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Beiranvand. La Roja b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean nh\u1edd m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7y may m\u1eafn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng t\u01b0\u1edfng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap t\u00e2m l\u00fd c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao b\u00ean ph\u00eda TBN \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa v\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, song th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nIran \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m sau b\u00e0n thua, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ti\u1ec1m \u1ea9n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t v\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00fat 62 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Saeid Ezatolahi \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi TBN, song tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u00e3 lao c\u1ea3 ra ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n \u00f4m nhau sung s\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00ec tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u1ee3p l\u1ec7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Iran kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh t\u1ec9nh v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a TBN. H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao c\u1ee7a Iran li\u00ean t\u1ee5c khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a La Roja \u1edf v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf nguy hi\u1ec3m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGerard Pique l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ecf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed khi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 bi\u00ean ph\u1ea3i b\u00f3 v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nhung tinh huong len bong cua Iran khien TBN gap rat nhieu kho khan\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Iran khi\u1ebfn TBN g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/vat-va-bao-ve-chien-thang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Iran khi\u1ebfn TBN g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00fat 82, Pique su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 khi d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng b\u1ecb Amiri x\u1ecf h\u00e1ng v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t v\u00e0o ph\u00eda trong, may cho TBN l\u00e0 Taremi l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111i v\u1ecdt x\u00e0 ngang.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb bi\u00ean c\u1ee7a Iran khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 TBN g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Ramos v\u00e0 Pique kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 li\u00ean l\u1ea1c c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft trong khi \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 bi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao t\u1ed1t. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 may m\u1eafn m\u1edbi gi\u00fap TBN gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a TBN c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Iran ch\u01a1i quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t v\u00e0 qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u00e3 xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1eb7n nh\u1eefng c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00ec La Roja l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng thi\u1ebfu quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-iran-vs-tay-ban-nha-421-189095.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Iran vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span> gi\u00fap La Roja c\u00f3 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 tr\u1eadn, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 B\u0110N. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i Sergio Ramos v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Ma R\u1ed1c, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1nh c\u1eeda v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo \u0111ang r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc TBN, song n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111ang g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Iran 0-1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha<span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span><br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Iran 0-1 Tay Ban Nha\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Iran 0-1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/Thong-so-Iran.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Iran 0-1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"394","checkdouble":"189120"},{"date":"06:28 21/06","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (21/6/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-2162018.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay 21/6 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u00f4ng tin ng\u00e0y gi\u1edd c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 di\u1ec5n ra h\u00f4m nay v\u00e0 \u0111\u00eam/r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y mai.</h2><div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vck-world-cup-2018/lich-thi-dau-41.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/3/Lich_thi_dau_World_Cup_2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vck-world-cup-2018/lich-thi-dau-41.html\"> L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u VCK World Cup 2018 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t</span><br>\r\nC\u1eadp nh\u1eadt nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u VCK World Cup 2018 t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 14.6 \u0111\u1ebfn 15.7.2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay 21-6-2018 v\u00e0 r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y mai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay 21-6-2018 v\u00e0 r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y mai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/Ivan-Rakitic-phat-bieu-ve-Lionel-Messi-hinh-an