;\">22/06 01:00</div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">Argentina - Croatia</td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">VTV3</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"393","checkdouble":"189124"},{"date":"06:41 21/06","title":"Nghi \u00e1n tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i m\u1ea5t li\u00ean l\u1ea1c VAR tr\u1eadn B\u0110N 1-0 Morocco","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/21/nghi-an-trong-tai-mat-lien-lac-var-tran-bdn-10-morocco.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Mark Geiger \u0111\u00e3 thay b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0m \u1edf ph\u00fat 85 sau khi trung v\u1ec7 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha Pepe \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea1m tay r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba \u1edf ph\u00fat 80. Nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea1i sao VAR l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng can thi\u1ec7p?\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ng\u01b0\u1eddi M\u1ef9 v\u00e0 t\u1ed5 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5 tr\u00e1ch VAR trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Morocco t\u1ed1i qua. Hai t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea1m tay c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi nh\u1eadn.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"S\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i tr\u1eadn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Morocco khi m\u1ea5t VAR h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"S\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i tr\u1eadn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Morocco khi m\u1ea5t VAR h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/Geiger-in-PORvMAR.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Mark Geiger</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 11 Bernardo \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea1m tay s\u00e1t khu v\u1ef1c 16m50, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e1ng n\u00f3i nh\u1ea5t ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 pha ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u1eb1ng tay c\u1ee7a Pepe \u1edf ph\u00fat 80. T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfu \u0111i chi\u1ebfu l\u1ea1i tr\u00ean truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u VAR l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng \u1edf t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 5 ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3 th\u00ec c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 khi \u00f4ng Mark Geiger ch\u1ea1y ra ngo\u00e0i thay b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0m li\u00ean l\u1ea1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00fat 85, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh nh\u1edd tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i th\u1ee9 4 \u0111\u1ed5i thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb li\u00ean l\u1ea1c r\u1ed3i nhanh ch\u00f3ng cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c. \u0110\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 90+1, \u00f4ng Geiger ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Morocco \u0111\u1ec3 tay ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t chi ti\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 khi tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd \u1edf ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n b\u00ean kia ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u1ebfn n\u00f3i nh\u1ecf v\u1edbi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ng\u01b0\u1eddi M\u1ef9. Gi\u1ea3 thuy\u1ebft n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i c\u00e0ng \u0111\u00fang khi m\u00e0 c\u00e1c tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd \u0111\u1ec1u li\u00ean l\u1ea1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi nhau v\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i th\u1ee9 4 \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0m thay th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a cho \u00f4ng Geiger.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean B\u0110N \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i tr\u1eadn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Morocco. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Morocco \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfu n\u1ea1i t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Pepe \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea1m tay nh\u01b0ng v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, HLV Renard Herve \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i\u00ean ti\u1ebft khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u1ea3nh t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00f3. \u00d4ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f2i can thi\u1ec7p VAR nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f4ng t\u00e2m m\u00e0 n\u00f3i th\u00ec ch\u00ednh Ronaldo c\u0169ng m\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf v\u00ec VAR \u1edf ph\u00fat 84, 1 ph\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed5i b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0m. S\u1ed1 7 c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ng\u00e1n ch\u00e2n trong v\u00e0o c\u1ea5m m\u00e0 pha chi\u1ebfu l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, Ronaldo c\u00f2n ra hi\u1ec7u can thi\u1ec7p VAR y chang \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o.<br>\r\n<h2>C\u00e1c tin b\u00e0i h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 1-0 Morocco\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bo-dao-nha-len-dinh-the-gioi-bang-thu-bong-da-khong-yeu-thuong-noi-421-189104.html\">B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha: L\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi b\u1eb1ng th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng y\u00eau th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1ed5i?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tiep-tuc-ghi-ban-sieu-sao-ronaldo-noi-gi-421-189102.html\">Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n, si\u00eau sao Ronaldo n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/amrabat-phat-bieu-ve-cong-nghe-var-421-189101.html\">Sao Ma R\u1ed1c g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c: \u201cVAR l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 v\u00f4 d\u1ee5ng\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bi-loai-som-o-world-cup-2018-hlv-ma-roc-noi-gi-421-189100.html\">B\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i s\u1edbm \u1edf World Cup 2018 HLV Ma R\u1ed1c n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-bo-dao-nha-10-ma-roc-khac-biet-o-dang-cap-421-189099.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 1-0 Ma R\u1ed1c: Kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-santos-phat-bieu-sau-tran-bdn-10-ma-roc-421-189098.html\">HLV B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n Ma R\u1ed1c?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-dau-bo-dao-nha-10-ma-roc-421-189097.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 1-0 Ma R\u1ed1c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-bo-dao-nha-vs-ma-roc-ronaldo-lai-toa-sang-nhung-421-189093.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 1-0 Ma R\u1ed1c: Ronaldo l\u1ea1i t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, nh\u01b0ng\u2026</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"392","checkdouble":"189125"},{"date":"16:23 20/06","title":"Juventus b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t cho Real v\u00e0 Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/7/13/miralem-pjanic-juventus-2.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Juventus ra gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Pjanic l\u00ean t\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u Euro. H\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ec1n h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 khi m\u00e0 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i theo \u0111u\u1ed5i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m n\u00e0y bao g\u1ed3m Real Madrid v\u00e0 Barcelona.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pjanic \u201c\u0111\u1eaft kh\u00e1ch\u201d tr\u00ean TTCN</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Juventus t\u1eeb AS Roma v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 32 tri\u1ec7u Euro m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2016, Miralem Pjanic l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng. Anh l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa Bianconeri su\u1ed1t 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Pjanic trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Juventus l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ai s\u00e1nh b\u1eb1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng Pjanic, l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c Juventus b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. L\u1ea5y v\u00ed d\u1ee5 l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua. Tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa \u201cB\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0\u201d kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng khai th\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus ra gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Pjanic l\u00ean t\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u Euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Juventus ra gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Pjanic l\u00ean t\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u Euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/7/13/miralem-pjanic-juventus-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Juventus ra gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Pjanic l\u00ean t\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u Euro</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Pjanic, h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 anh. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/juventus-tu-choi-ban-sao-khung-cho-man-city-voi-gia-50-trieu-bang-172-187858.html\" target=\"_blank\">Juventus t\u1eebng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n sao kh\u1ee7ng cho Man City v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span>. M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, c\u1ea3 Real Madrid v\u00e0 Barcelona \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 cao</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Juventus th\u1eeba hi\u1ec3u t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Miralem Pjanic v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra \u0111i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. T\u1edd Tuttosport m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0a tin Juventus ra gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Pjanic \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 80 tri\u1ec7u Euro (t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 70,4 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Andres Iniesta chia tay Barca\" title=\"tien ve Andres Iniesta chia tay Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/21/De-Jong-khong-muon-toi-Barca-trong-tuong-lai-gan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Barca \u0111ang c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay Iniesta</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Barca \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1t m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao sau khi Andres Iniesta sang Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u201cd\u01b0\u1ee1ng gi\u00e0\u201d. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00fang ra \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n Andre Gomes, Denis Suarez \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf khi \u0111\u01b0a h\u1ecd v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 Barca h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang trong \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00edn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Barca ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1ea3 t\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Pjanic. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Juventus \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u201cc\u00e2u gi\u1edd\u201d \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00fd mu\u1ed1n. H\u1ecd tin n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia ch\u1eadm ch\u00e2n, \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Real Madrid c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng. R\u1ed3i c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 Man City hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang c\u00e1ch Pjanic s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u0169 50 tri\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Juventus tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-co-doi-thu-lon-vu-sao-bu-juventus-172-187781.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/23/Monaco-muon-dua-Gonzalo-Higuain-roi-Juventus-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-co-doi-thu-lon-vu-sao-bu-juventus-172-187781.html\">Chelsea c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn v\u1ee5 sao b\u1ef1 Juventus</span><br>\r\n<span>Sau Chelsea, t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t Monaco c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Gonzalo Higuain r\u1eddi Juventus, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-juventus-len-ke-hoach-rut-ruot-mu-172-188254.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/24/hlv-juventus-len-ke-hoach-rut-ruot-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-juventus-len-ke-hoach-rut-ruot-mu-172-188254.html\">HLV Juventus l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u201cr\u00fat ru\u1ed9t\u201d MU</span><br>\r\n<span>Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Anthony Martial c\u1ee7a MU v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. HLV Massimiliano Allegri \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"391","checkdouble":"189062"}]}